# Copy to apps/edge/.dev.vars and fill in for local `wrangler dev`.
# Do NOT commit `.dev.vars` — it is gitignored at the repo root.
#
# No worker secrets are required yet. Future read-only Polymarket access uses
# the public Gamma API (no auth). Anything that signs or moves funds belongs
# in services/core (the Rust service), never here.
#
# Reserved names (uncomment when introduced):
# CORE_SERVICE_URL=http://127.0.0.1:8787
